::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
#....Setup....

setwd("C:/Github Projects/601_Spring_2023/posts/_data")

library(tidyr)
library(tidyverse)
library(dplyr)
library(utils)

#.... Read in birds.csv ....
birds <- read.csv("birds.csv")
View(birds)
```
:::

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
#....Isolate Variables with Select().....
birds %>% 
  select(Area, Item, Year, Value) %>% 
  View()

#..... Summary .....
birds %>% 
  select(Area, Item, Year, Value) %>% 
  summary()
```
